  <description>
    <p>Convertidor is a handy and high precision application for converting units of measurement.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Conversion of 300+ units of measurement.</li>
      <li>Instant and accurate (synchronous) unit conversion.</li>
      <li>Control of calculation accuracy.</li>
      <li>Intuitive and user-friendly interface.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

